properties.areaDesc: Grand Marais to Taconite Harbor MN; Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN; Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN; Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 15 at 4:07PM CST until January 16 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 knots with gusts up to 35
knots and waves up to 3 feet expected.

* WHERE...Grand Portage to Grand Marais MN, Grand Marais to
Taconite Harbor MN, Taconite Harbor to Silver Bay Harbor MN
and Silver Bay Harbor to Two Harbors MN.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM CST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Anyone operating a smaller vessel should avoid navigating in
hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM CST THURSDAY
